data.description: This vibrant beauty is ready for a new owner's attention. The rare heart of Portland location, RM2 zoning possibilities, near by shops and restaurants, fantastic floor plan and Victorian flair will be sure to get your imagination stirring. Most period hardware, mill work, built-ins and kitchen cabinets are still here. Seller to make no repairs. **TENANT TO BE OUT OF THE PROPERTY SOON**
